==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# (''[[dressage]]'') A [[leap]] of a [[horse]], as between two [[pillar]]s, or on a straight line, so that when his four feet are in the air, he shows only the shoes of his hind feet, without jerking out. 

